name: AARPToday'sTips–Briefing
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Start your weekdays with AARP for the latest news and tips for people age 50-plus. We’ll break down what you need to know about your health, money and personal fulfillment in five minutes or less, five days a week.

Note: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
